name: Nate Fuller
title: Blogging in the 16th century
text: Look at me! I'm blogging on sheepskin that's being read out in all the nearby towns by their town criers.

name: Luis Moraguez
title: Does blogging with a graph count as telework?
text: I'm blogging with a telegraph. People just don't seem to understand when I ask them to like and subscribe.

name: Ahna Cecil
title: Mike TeeVee's got nothing on me
text: This new Television thing is super cool. I'm so hip that I decided to combine the words "blog" and "video" to create the first ever vlog.

name: Nicole Ely
title: Today is the tomorrow you were so worried about yesterday
text: The future's cool and all but people still think they're hot shit because they have a blog and it is so annoying!
